<HEAD>Jury Gets Case in Escape, Witness Murder Case</HEAD>
<HEAD>Eds: LEADS with 12 grafs to UPDATE with guilty verdicts returned;
reax from prosecutor. Picks up 7th graf, `In their ...'; Drops first reference
to Wright and Flora in subsequent grafs to conform. ADDS 1 graf after last
